description: Veena George instructs health department for Alappuzha bird flu outbreak action. Surveillance in nearby areas, 'One Health' committees strengthened. Health guidelines followed, doctor consultation advised for respiratory issues.
title: Bird flu: Invoke steps under health act, Kerala min to officials

description: 15-year-old boy and 9-year-old sister found dead in Pandav Nagar home. Father dead on railway track. Mother unconscious. Accused had liver disease, hired helpers at tea stall. Key maker opened locked door.
title: Siblings found murdered day after dad's death in Delhi

description: Sunrisers Hyderabad's explosive power hitting has astonished Sachin Tendulkar. In the match against Delhi Capitals, SRH dominated with Travis Head, Abhishek Sharma and Shahbaz Ahmed scoring at a blistering pace to post a total in excess of 260 once again . Delhi Capitals were kept in the chase by Jake Fraser-McGurk and Abishek Porel but succumbed to scoreboard pressure in the end.
title: 'What is it with SRH!' Asks a baffled Sachin Tendulkar

description: Witnessing the carnage in the Delhi Capitals vs Sunrisers Hyderabad high-scoring IPL match with record-breaking batting performances, former SA pacer Dale Steyn praised bowlers standing out in such games. MI pacer Bumrah leads the list of wicket-takers this season with 13 wickets in 7 matches at an economy rate of just 5.96.
title: Watching IPL carnage, Steyn tells why Bumrah is a rare gem

description: A man died on Friday after setting himself on fire outside the New York courthouse where Donald Trump's landmark hush-money trial was concluding jury selection. However, officials stated that he did not seem to have been targeting Trump. The man burned for several minutes in full view of television cameras that were set up outside the courthouse, where the first-ever criminal trial of a former US president is being held.
title: Man who set himself on fire outside Trump trial in New York dies
